OL,3,CStill unidentified: 45 years since
OL,4,Cbody found in woods
OL,6,FAn appeal has been launched to help
OL,7,Fidentify the body of a man found in
OL,8,Fremote woods exactly 45 years ago. The
OL,9,Fmystery of the 'Glamorgan Man' has
OL,10,Fbaffled authorities for nearly five
OL,11,Fdecades.
OL,13,FOn December 9, 1979, the skeletal
OL,14,Fremains of a man were found in Rheola
OL,15,FForest, near Resolven. He is believed
OL,16,Fto have died between nine and 18
OL,17,Fmonths previously.
OL,19,FIt has been thought over the years
OL,20,Fthat he might be a visitor from South
OL,21,FAfrica.
