OL,3,CStill unidentified: 45 years since
OL,4,Cbody found in woods
OL,6,FOn his body was a Salvation Testament
OL,7,Fwhich bore the name D MALAN and a
OL,8,Fpartial address in Randburg, South
OL,9,FAfrica. Much of the evidence points
OL,10,Ftowards him having been from South
OL,11,FAfrica, or having had a link to the
OL,12,Fcountry.
OL,14,FVolunteer investigators with Locate
OL,15,FInternational, a charity which looks
OL,16,Finto cold cases of missing and
OL,17,Funidentified people, have been working
OL,18,Fon the case of Glamorgan Man, as he is
OL,19,Fknown, for the past four years.
